## Spec Context
Data model interfaces:

```typescript
interface CareerNode {
  id: string;
  type: 'role' | 'company' | 'skill' | 'project' | 'education' | 'certification';
  label: string;
  category?: string;
  startDate?: string;
  endDate?: string;
  proficiency?: number;
  description?: string;
  url?: string;
}

interface CareerEdge {
  source: string;
  target: string;
  type: 'worked-at' | 'used-skill' | 'built-with' | 'earned-at' | 'requires' | 'part-of';
}

interface CareerData {
  nodes: CareerNode[];
  edges: CareerEdge[];
}
```

Existing file exports: SiteMeta, SocialLink, Project, SkillCategory, GitHubConfig, SiteData, getSiteData().
Add: CareerNode, CareerEdge, CareerData, getCareerData().
getCareerData() imports from '../../content/career-data.json'.

Keep CareerData separate from SiteData (not nested in site.json).

IMPORTANT: No Co-Authored-By in commits.

## Spec Context
Current index.astro imports Skills and renders:
```astro
import Skills from '../components/Skills.astro';
{site.skills && site.skills.length > 0 && <Skills skills={site.skills} revealIndex={3} />}
```

Replace with:
```astro
import KnowledgeGraph from '../components/KnowledgeGraph.astro';
import { getCareerData } from '../data/site';
const careerData = getCareerData();

{site.skills && site.skills.length > 0 && <KnowledgeGraph skills={site.skills} careerData={careerData} revealIndex={3} />}
```

Keep all other imports and components unchanged. Skills import can be removed.

IMPORTANT: No Co-Authored-By in commits.

