```

Add after the clear block:
```javascript
if (typeof window.__graphFilter === 'function') {
  window.__graphFilter(keyword || '');
}
```

And in the clear/reset block, add:
```javascript
if (typeof window.__graphFilter === 'function') {
  window.__graphFilter('');
}
```

Keep the existing .skills__item and .card filtering intact — they serve as fallback and for non-graph elements.

